{"type":"message","id":"730f1f6e","parentId":"82a3f873","timestamp":"2026-04-02T15:45:06.200Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The wiki space ID is 7615846908665285857, not the one provided. But the user gave me a URL `https://my.feishu.cn/wiki/MVjqwq2pGi8GVKkXOn0c9VpNnTc`. The `MVjqwq2pGi8GVKkXOn0c9VpNnTc` is likely a node token, not a space ID. Let me try to get info about that node.\n\nActually, let me try to create the document in the wiki space. The wiki node token might work with the node creation. Let me first try to get the node info, then create the document there.\n\n\nLooking at the URL structure more carefully, that token after `/wiki/` is a node token from Feishu's base64 variant encoding. I should use the wiki write skill to properly handle this.","thinkingSignature":"db88a67be90c9b693fb07bb0696e939048e8053f647bc904fa82a3b0a4215439"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_z7na7zec0xnf_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/shared-skills/feishu-wiki-write/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5-highspeed","usage":{"input":1652,"output":220,"cacheRead":37026,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":38898,"cost":{"input":0.0009912,"output":0.0005279999999999999,"cacheRead":0.0022215599999999996,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0037407599999999997}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775144701978}}
{"type":"message","id":"70152494","parentId":"730f1f6e","timestamp":"2026-04-02T15:45:06.212Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_z7na7zec0xnf_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: feishu-wiki-write\ndescription: |\n  写入飞书知识库文档。根据文件名和内容自动选择最合适的目录创建子文档并写入 Markdown 内容。\n  知识库：AI知识库 (space_id: 7615846908665285857)\n---\n\n# feishu_wiki_write\n\n将 Markdown 内容写入飞书知识库。根据文件名和内容关键词分析，自动选择最合适的文档目录下创建子文档。\n\n## 目标知识库\n\n- **名称**: AI 知识库  \n- **Space ID**: 7615846908665285857\n- **URL**: https://my.feishu.cn/wiki/settings/7615846908665285857\n\n## 参数\n\n### filename（可选）\n文件名（不含扩展名）。用于：\n1. 作为文档标题\n2. 分析文件类型和分类\n\n### content（必填）\nMarkdown 内容，要写入文档的内容。使用 Lark-flavored Markdown 格式。\n\n## 工作流程\n\n1. 在知识库根目录创建新文档\n2. 写入 Markdown 内容\n3. 返回文档链接\n\n## 当前状态\n\n⚠️ **权限待添加**：应用需要以下权限才能读写知识库：\n- `wiki:space:readonly` - 读取知识库\n- `wiki:node:create` - 创建知识库文档  \n- `wiki:node:update` - 更新知识库文档\n\n## 返回值\n\n- **doc_url**: 文档访问链接\n- **doc_id**: 文档 ID  \n- **node_token**: 知识库节点 token\n\n## 示例\n\n```json\n{\n  \"filename\": \"API设计规范\",\n  \"content\": \"# API 设计规范\\n\\n## 概述\\n\\n本文档定义了 REST API 的设计标准。\"\n}\n```\n\n## 注意事项\n\n- 知识库 space_id: `7615846908665285857`\n- 需要在飞书开放平台开通 `wiki:space:readonly` 和 `wiki:node:create` 权限\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775144706206}}
