{"type":"message","id":"f2dde6b8","parentId":"45bfa73d","timestamp":"2026-04-02T15:47:22.836Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The document has been created and updated successfully. Let me provide the user with the document link.","thinkingSignature":"1b7dc7e8a4abe477e935af1390287047e4e54f45794f60aa1043c5e09914799b"},{"type":"text","text":"搞定啦！🦐 文档已写入知识库，链接：\n\n👉 https://my.feishu.cn/wiki/SP3SdE85PoVYtHxVdj9c0GxMn1e\n\n---\n\n**汇报一下我写了啥：**\n\n一共收录了 **12种提示词框架**，每个框架包含：\n\n- ✅ 含义解析（原理 + 使用场景 + 最佳实践）\n- ✅ 示例一（侧重一个场景）\n- ✅ 示例二（侧重另一个场景）\n\n| 框架 | 最适场景 |\n|------|---------|\n| CoT | 数学/逻辑推理 |\n| Zero-shot CoT | 通用快速任务 |\n| Few-shot | 模式学习类任务 |\n| ReAct | Agent/多步工具调用 |\n| CRISPE | 专业角色扮演 |\n| BROKE | 商业目标导向任务 |\n| ICIP | 结构化文档生成 |\n| CREATE | 创意内容创作 |\n| SCOPE | 企业文档规范 |\n| APE | 快速起草 |\n| DECRIBE | 复杂边界任务 |\n| COAST | 精准沟通传达 |\n\n文档末尾还附了一张**横向对比速查表**，方便按需选用。如果需要补充某个框架或者调整示例方向，随时说～"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5-highspeed","usage":{"input":9057,"output":273,"cacheRead":37026,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":46356,"cost":{"input":0.0054342,"output":0.0006552,"cacheRead":0.0022215599999999996,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00831096}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775144837746}}
